config MTK_NFC_SUPPORT
	tristate "MediaTek NFC driver"
	default n
	help
	  Y means NFC_MT6605 define if use Mediatek NFC Function to provide reader
	  Card emulation or P2P function. If you are not sure about this, set n.
	  Y means NFC_MT6605 define if use Mediatek NFC Function to provide reader
